[{"_key":"5eed3edf-4be2-4bc3-a7e3-a70ef30eba53","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"201c557c-0acf-4b82-947a-3f1ecb0cb7cb","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"# 看護助手と看護師の仕事の違いを徹底比較"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"655d9973-e879-4100-a5f7-fb77d20f7ef5","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"600cefef-c311-4d45-b742-b05139f3c3cd","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"最大の違い：医療行為の可否と資格の有無"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"f90086fa-0dc3-4d5f-814a-1ba4516b338a","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"46ff6b4a-407a-4b24-a2fa-fe85c81fb472","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"看護助手と看護師を分ける最も大きな違いは、「医療行為ができるかどうか」です。これは、保有する資格の違いに基づいています。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"80fbc98e-0c9d-43eb-b9d4-fb7fc77fbe07","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"700422d6-2dc0-4311-be9a-1bf89f09db28","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"**看護師**: 国家資格である「看護師免許」が必要です。医師の指示のもと、あるいは自らの判断で、採血、注射、点滴などの医療行為を行うことができます。"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"block-gyoqvqcpl","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"span-0oqoynhus","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"💼 転職・求人をお探しの方へ： "},{"_key":"span-u6sxy1pou","_type":"span","marks":["link-w0e7q6jwc"],"text":"介護職・看護助手の求人なら「ヒューマンライフケア」"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"link-w0e7q6jwc","_type":"link","href":"//af.moshimo.com/af/c/click?a_id=5207863&p_id=6140&pc_id=17239&pl_id=78717"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"d334e086-506f-4a56-bcce-9b564f29515d","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"05211246-6b33-41fd-a69c-666939de6df4","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"**看護助手**: 必須の資格はありません。そのため、医療行為を行うことは法律で固く禁じられています。業務は、看護師の指示のもとで行う「補助業務」に限られます。"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"block-zzltgrco6","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"span-ka4n5ls1k","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"💼 看護助手の仕事内容について詳しく知りたい方は、こちらの記事もご覧ください： "},{"_key":"span-ka4n5ls1k-link","_type":"span","marks":["link-ctg7a38an"],"text":"看護助手とは？病院での具体的な役割を徹底解説"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"link-ctg7a38an","_type":"link","href":"/posts/nursing-assistant-hospital-roles-explained"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"block-1760792966394-p0gcd1cgg","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"span-1760792966394-i26ker74k","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"📖 関連記事: "},{"_key":"span-link-1760792966394-5xss4z8o2","_type":"span","marks":["link-1760792966394-5qxtxxznh"],"text":"看護助手に資格は必要？未経験でも働ける？"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"link-1760792966394-5qxtxxznh","_type":"link","href":"/posts/nursing-assistant-qualifications-needed"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"block-1760792966394-nhmi4e2rr","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"span-1760792966394-gykfrrln3","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"📖 関連記事: "},{"_key":"span-link-1760792966394-4byjbkdky","_type":"span","marks":["link-1760792966394-orbjw0x09"],"text":"看護助手の転職成功マニュアル｜求人の選び方から面接対策まで"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"link-1760792966394-orbjw0x09","_type":"link","href":"/posts/nursing-assistant-job-change-manual"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"5bd925f4-60ab-40d7-a2f4-45e19612f61c","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"efabd99d-fb53-4802-ad09-a520c07b51a5","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"業務内容の違い"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"eb33ffef-3119-423f-965b-8636c9720623","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"2892cd2c-2f95-45a3-8926-683592d96c30","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"医療行為の可否によって、それぞれの業務内容は大きく異なります。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"block-1760792966394-0praa5i8t","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"span-1760792966394-zp2dyz2m8","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"📖 関連記事: "},{"_key":"span-link-1760792966394-b2h8ermbu","_type":"span","marks":["link-1760792966394-8h9thv4yl"],"text":"看護助手の仕事内容を新人でもわかりやすく解説"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"link-1760792966394-8h9thv4yl","_type":"link","href":"/posts/nursing-assistant-job-description-beginners"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"81dfcb77-d676-47df-923e-ea3b67bb4d6b","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"7830229a-8fc2-47a6-bb33-477ddffde4a0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"看護師の主な業務"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"21a67b69-9aa4-4a60-bda3-f3e636a6a514","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"c7313d3b-3bf7-46d1-9f21-4d10615749d5","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"看護師は、専門的な知識と技術に基づき、患者さんの診療や治療に直接関わります。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"4d76f301-7250-4e00-abe3-e6e340c032fe","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"cf6d6b3d-db78-4aab-9db9-d1fcb5190652","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"**診療の補助**: 医師の指示に基づく採血、注射、点滴、与薬など。"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"01f70337-4854-4645-9b5e-630504d56f18","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"5c3dd996-8d28-4ece-b863-c9dcdde3b3db","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"**療養上の世話**: 専門的な知識に基づく健康状態のアセスメント（評価）、ケア計画の立案、褥瘡（床ずれ）の処置など。"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"f9736145-647a-4ae4-854d-c4339505263a","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"513ca7bb-2e5e-4f14-a7dd-8eca1218ed99","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"**看護計画の立案と評価**: 患者さん一人ひとりの状態に合わせた看護計画を立て、その実施と評価を行います。"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"5d4fe7b2-a258-4920-9b48-050b8d1016c0","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"882d7632-5a02-4b34-9b90-b3f02a1a5d20","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"**他職種との連携**: 医師やリハビリスタッフなど、チーム医療のコーディネート役を担います。"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"207189d7-c03e-462b-9adc-817f11568d7d","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"32777fe9-48e3-4dbe-ba38-a9b4174a6da6","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"看護助手の主な業務"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"0705a9f4-5e80-4453-8768-23d8951fbff3","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"541e0760-2af9-482c-add5-feb038226fae","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"看護助手は、看護師の指示のもと、患者さんの療養生活を支える身の回りのお世話や、環境整備が主な仕事です。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"4966320c-7e55-4cd9-a4f9-6695aa39a6ff","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"3af17753-e6c0-4f07-97a5-539eaf1675d8","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"**身体介助**: 食事、入浴、排泄の介助、体位変換、移乗の補助など。"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"28d4c84c-d8d6-4a57-92e0-804e067fe8f9","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"568df62a-e27f-4de3-8da0-2ea08488e7d4","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"**環境整備**: ベッドメイキング、病室の清掃、リネン交換など。"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"cba98a56-22d0-4c6f-8521-c61fe89b2b1a","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"a8f3a6b7-eae2-434d-bdf9-6bb3f119e36a","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"**看護師の補助**: 医療器具の洗浄・準備、メッセンジャー業務、書類整理など。"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"block-hlk47c2ls-intro-b33900f4-d6a6-4f79-8b76-2aa663306a58","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"span-58c3ouwgd","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"✨ やりがいのある仕事をお探しの方へ： "}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"block-aygncaegl","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"span-rqdxd50co","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"💼 看護助手の仕事内容について詳しく知りたい方は、こちらの記事もご覧ください： "},{"_key":"span-rqdxd50co-link","_type":"span","marks":["link-6r8pbqz6d"],"text":"看護助手とは？病院での具体的な役割を徹底解説"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"link-6r8pbqz6d","_type":"link","href":"/posts/nursing-assistant-hospital-roles-explained"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"block-1760792966394-0gl5dfk58","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"span-1760792966394-szf07vw5p","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"📖 関連記事: "},{"_key":"span-link-1760792966394-30cx5ro4d","_type":"span","marks":["link-1760792966394-xpv7m6mvi"],"text":"看護助手の仕事内容を新人でもわかりやすく解説"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"link-1760792966394-xpv7m6mvi","_type":"link","href":"/posts/nursing-assistant-job-description-beginners"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"block-1760792966394-bafpqfsqs","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"span-1760792966394-nt9nltl8l","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"📖 関連記事: "},{"_key":"span-link-1760792966394-oirnu36pw","_type":"span","marks":["link-1760792966394-etjun9qq4"],"text":"看護助手のやりがいと達成感が得られる瞬間"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"link-1760792966394-etjun9qq4","_type":"link","href":"/posts/nursing-assistant-job-fulfillment"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"06fc2527-09f7-40d7-ab8d-fff48e2993b4","_type":"b