護師の方が手厚い傾向にあります。"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"48b162e7-302d-43a4-9b65-78d631f5916c","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"2171949d-f2ba-4a0a-b70d-ca44549ae09b","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"**キャリアパス**: 看護師は、認定看護師や専門看護師、管理職（看護師長など）といった明確なキャリアパスがあります。一方、看護助手からのキャリアアップとしては、介護福祉士や、看護師を目指すといった道が一般的です。"}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"block-1760792966394-xgtbknpdc","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"span-1760792966394-22bgn5czl","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"📖 関連記事: "},{"_key":"span-link-1760792966394-6zl4p0sic","_type":"span","marks":["link-1760792966394-xn4k1bnkm"],"text":"看護助手の夜勤はきつい？一晩の流れを紹介"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"link-1760792966394-xn4k1bnkm","_type":"link","href":"/posts/nursing-assistant-night-shift-hard"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"block-1760792966394-hpqe2jw9v","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"span-1760792966394-yl7jvt23a","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"📖 関連記事: "},{"_key":"span-link-1760792966394-a26krw7ty","_type":"span","marks":["link-1760792966394-5mmy7rl8b"],"text":"看護助手の平均給料はいくら？最新データまとめ"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"link-1760792966394-5mmy7rl8b","_type":"link","href":"/posts/nursing-assistant-average-salary-data"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"hrjxbpq7916","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"36m46z7pokq","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"看護助手ができないこと（重要）"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"yfeqmpy88lr","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"hglvelr6cm","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"看護助手は医療現場で重要な役割を担っていますが、医療行為を行うことはできません。患者さんの安全を守るため、以下の行為は法律で禁止されています。"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"53p9npvbv9l","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"opidkrjn39n","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"注射・点滴・採血などの医療処置"}],"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"6a4ibzoniji","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"apvtmaq5it8","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"薬の投与や管理"}],"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"dkgo016nedr","_type":"